Dependences
===========
* UNIX dependences 
    coreutils or equivalent (tail date echo sort cat mkdir rm env touch)
    grep      or equivalent (grep)
    bash      or equivalent (sh)
* Other dependences
    tar       or equivalent (tar)
    curl      or equivalent (curl)
    zenity    or rquivalent (zenity)
I have just tested with GNU ones.


Installation of CLI
==================
Copy flash-tool to any folder in your PATH variable and make it executable.

Installation of GUI
==================

Install zenity and trow flash-tool.desktop in /usr/share/applications/
or ~/.local/share/applications


